parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx^.This mansion is nestled against Casula Forest. The forest is very thick here…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.Shit… It might be difficult to track them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Send three of your officers into the forest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.We’re going to need to post up and watch the exits.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Lillian’s safety is of the utmost importance right now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoBaEx>.Greenly, Duffy, Alapopskalius, go chase after them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BoAnEx<.The rest of you, come with me. We’re not letting that lunatic come back here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaHaOp.Boy, am I glad you showed up, Miss Bhatt.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnDe.David, I thought I told you to wait for backup.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DaAnOp.I’m too close to retirement to let you get me killed, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx>.Please let the others know about our new guests.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.It’s okay, Lillian. It seems your father has left you more than just a mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.What are you going to do? Are they going to come back for treasure?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.My father has many treasures, but I am not aware of any treasure room…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.At least, nothing that’s more valuable than what is easily seen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.He’s a Guild leader. He’d be looking for artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.I feel my safety has been compromised.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I hate to be the bearer of worse news, but I found Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaOp.And that’s bad news? Where is she?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiWoCl.She’s still here? That can’t be true. What more would she want from my family?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.Damn! Do you think she’s linked to that Guild guy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I don’t know… Something strange is happening.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.This will sound crazy, but Madalyn disappeared…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.The forest is very thick. She could have easily evaded your search efforts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It wasn’t like that. I was right up next to her… We had her cornered…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Then she just went up in a puff of smoke.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.She did something… She had a smoke bomb.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.No! She was naked. She didn’t have anything on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Trust me. Madalyn is doing something… supernatural.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.I didn’t take you for the type to believe such things.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Something is going on in the forest and I need to figure it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.Maybe you should tell us what you know, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnEx.You knew that woman… and she knew that Guild dude.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.You have a connection to the woman, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.That’s Nellie… She’s the mother of a friend of mine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErAnDe.You talk about trust, yet you have this connection to the Guild that you didn’t tell us about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.It’s not like that. I just met the woman. I didn’t know anything about her connection to the Guild.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.I’m sure 1Hero has good intentions. I trust him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m going to figure this out. But until I do, you’re going to need to trust us…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.We’ll make sure no one enters your home, Lillian.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiSaDe.I don’t like the idea of having surveillance. But I understand.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiFrOp.Thank you, Miss Bhatt, for showing up when you did. I could almost call your timing divine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Well, 1Hero, it seems you were onto something, after all.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFlDe.Stop it. I’m sure working for me can be infuriating.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeFrEx.But I give credit where it’s due, and you saw something I missed. Good job.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.You have the green light to watch her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Gain her trust, and find out what she knows.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.About everything. Duncan Helmer didn’t break in here for no reason.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We need to know who she really is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Sure thing. And thank you. I won’t let you down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.We’ll need to throw Lillian off about our suspicions. Follow my lead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "H2MaAg>.Get back or the commissioner gets a bullet in the head!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlDe.I knew I could depend on you, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnOp.You have a lot of nerve, showing up here. Expect to assassinate me?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.Listen to the lady. She saved my life and probably yours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We followed your goon through the old bunker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaEx.Uh, yeah. We totally tracked him down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuMaAgNo1.That son of a bitch! Trying to get revenge on me, I’m sure.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.What the hell do we do now? Pretend he got away?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuHaEx.I say we kill Morgan and then bury both bodies in the forest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdMaExNo1^.Duncan! Your obsession with revenge is going to lead to my downfall.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnEx.Do you want to sleep at night, Duncan?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDeNo4.Haha! You’re the least of my concerns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElAnEx.I have nothing left. You’ve backed me into a corner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnEx^.Leave us, Duncan… I’ll make the girl whole.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.How much money are we talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuFlDe.I’ve got a gold treasure she can take.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdAnOp^.Tell me you didn’t bring a piece of Nadia’s treasure here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.I never touched it. I know the rules.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuAnEx.We’re even now, Morgan… But you cross me again and I’ll double the price on your head.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DuHaOp.Come on, Victor. Time to have you put into the ground.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoCl.Wait… How do you have the power to order Duncan around?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.This is my operation now… Charles went crazy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElWoOp.I suspected something was wrong with him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.You’re lucky he didn’t get you killed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.How long have you been planning this… takeover?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.The Guild was doomed to fall… Quite literally cursed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx^.Thanks to you and Nellie, I’ve managed to put together something new.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdBaEx^.This operation should be run by one individual… Not twelve.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.You and I are going to be very powerful, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.He has no choice. It’s either die, or be led by me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaOp.If the Guild’s not dead… Am I still on the payroll?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp^.I could use a woman with your beauty.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElFlEx.I can fight. I’m damn good at it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Ella? You’ve got a ticket out. Why would you want back in?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaOp.The Guild is finally under the rule of a female… This should be interesting.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.It’s a honeypot… Don’t go thinking you’ll be stealing artifacts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFrEx^.Nellie and you have been integral to this operation, but I could always use more loyal associates.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaEx.I killed that hitman. Isn’t that enough?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.I have my own way of testing those around me… just ask 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.Come to my office Monday. We can go over the findings there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Oh, uhh. There was a report of suspicious activity, but all is clear.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaDe.It’s getting late. Are you still working?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McHaEx.Just heading out now. I’m looking forward to the weekend.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "LiBaEx.I assume the officer outside will be staying?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Yes. He’ll keep his eye peeled for anything suspicious.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlDe^.1Hero’s been telling me you’re helping him with his case.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx^.There’s something going on here… There’s a secret area in this mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We have an opportunity to find our way inside and see for ourselves what’s going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We just need you to distract the guards long enough for us to find the entrance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx^.We know where the eye… the key is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.We just have to figure out where to use it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.I can buy you some time. But you better hurry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.There’s a guard in the next room. I’ll pull him away and then the clock starts.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.I’m going to keep tabs on the transmitters. Don’t forget we’re in this together.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.You’re right. This isn’t over… It’s just the beginning.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiBaEx.I want to know what they are hiding.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "KiFlOp.See you around, 1Hero. Enjoy the news segment tonight.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I saw the Toma piece and a pentagram on the floor…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There were six hooded statues all surrounding it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoOp.What about the sound? Did you hear it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.No… If we’re going to figure out what’s being hidden down there, I’ll need to figure out a way to get deeper.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.The place is crawling with those leper dudes. It won’t be easy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoCl.I just hope to God I’m not some sort of planned sacrifice to Satan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.From the looks of things, the Toma pieces appear to be part of some ritual.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.I don’t know what it could be, but I can try and find out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErBaEx.If it is, I’ll see what I can find.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ErWoEx.You better leave too. Lillian might ask what we’ve been discussing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.This metal box is secured by a rusty lock and chain. Even if I had a key, it probably wouldn’t work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaOp.My hacksaw isn’t strong enough to saw through this lock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my diamond saw to cut through the chain!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But I might be able to pick the lock with the right tool.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.My lock pick is too weak for this one. I need something stronger.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Maybe I can use my lock pick to open it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I thought my dick was getting crushed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlOp^.You shot quite a lot of cum in my pussy, 1Hero.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.A warm reminder of the loyalty the two of you have for this new and improved operation.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlEx^.Stop by this evening… I’ll make sure you get your two million.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "AdFlExNo3^.Haha… Oh, 1Hero. There’s so much more than that.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ElHaEx.You killed Duncan’s henchman… Andrea is pulling the strings…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.You really think Duncan’s going to let this happen?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.No time to mess around. I need to find a hair from Lillian to open the rift.");
